BARBERTON – Dr Philemon Mankodi Marakalla was arrested for violating a protection order granted to his his wife. Read More: Doctor arrested for murder Capt Jabu Ndubane, Barberton police spokesman confirmed Marakalla’s arrest. He was arrested on Saturday for assaulting his wife with a hammer and also for violation of a protection order,” said Ndubane. Marakalla appeared before the Barberton Magistrate’s Court on Monday. He was released on a free bail. He will appear before the same court on June. 7.